# Faz 4: Permission System

## Goal

RBAC (direct role assignments) + ABAC (attribute rule engine) hybrid. PermissionResolverService Redis cache (5dk TTL). 4-katman enforcement (guard + decorator + ownership + field-level). Admin UI: roles, permissions matrix, role assignment, attribute rules.

## Bu fazın çalışma modeli (iterasyonlar)

`@54-phase-04-permission-system` + **“Faz 4 — İterasyon N”**. Çekirdek servisler önce, UI sonra.

### İterasyon 1 — Resolver + evaluator + PermissionGuard

**Hedef:** `permission-resolver.service`, `attribute-rule-evaluator.service`, `permission.guard`, DTO’lar, `Permission` enum/metadata paylaşımı; unit testler (cache’siz veya mock Redis).

**Minimum bağlam:** `docs/04_BACKEND_SPEC.md` Bölüm 6; `docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION.md` Bölüm 4 (kurallar).

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** Event tabanlı cache invalidation listener; admin React ekranları.

**Stop:** [ ] Resolver + evaluator + guard testleri yeşil. PR/onay.

### İterasyon 2 — Cache + invalidation + 4-katman integration

**Hedef:** Redis TTL, `role-cache-invalidation.listener`, `role-permission-management` atomik güncellemeler; 4-katman integration testleri (her katman ayrı senaryo); field-level serialization test.

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** Permission matrix UI, attribute rule builder UI.

**Stop:** [ ] Invalidation trigger testleri; [ ] 4-katman checklist tamam. PR/onay.

### İterasyon 3 — Admin UI (roller + matrix + attribute rules)

**Hedef:** Rol CRUD, permission matrix, attribute rule CRUD/builder, user role assignment bileşenleri.

**Minimum bağlam:** `docs/06_SCREEN_CATALOG.md` S-ROLE-*, S-PERMISSION-MATRIX, S-ATTR-RULE-*.

**Stop:** Faz 4 Done Definition + roadmap işareti.

