## Constraints

- Cache invalidation EventEmitter pattern (3 trigger: user role change, role permission change, attribute rule change)
- Attribute rules: OR between groups, AND within group
- Operators supported: equals, not_equals, contains, in, starts_with, ends_with
- Permission enum tek source of truth (`packages/shared-types`)
- Metadata zorunlu her Permission için
- 4-katman enforcement: hepsi implement

