- [ ] Attribute rule visual builder: group + condition CRUD
- [ ] 4-katman integration test — her katman ayrı test
- [ ] Field-level serialization test (actor permission'a göre field visible/null)

## Explicit Don'ts

- Pre-warming cache (MVP'de on-demand yeter)
- Complex ABAC policy language (OR/AND yeter)
- Time-based permissions (seasonal, schedule) — post-MVP
- Permission delegation (user assigns permissions to user) — admin only
- Role inheritance (hierarchical roles) — post-MVP

